metadata.name: Dracula Vampire Club # 1
metadata.description: The Dracula Vampire Club is a collection of 10,001 unique Dracula NFTs, unique digital collectibles that live on the Ethereum blockchain. The Dracula Vampire Club will hold regular meetings between its members, in small groups or larger in different areas around the world. Participation is allowed only to those who own an NFT from the Dracula collection. Dracula is a Vampire Club membership card and offers access to benefits only for members, the first is access to the WEB3 platform which can bring you close to the secret empire of specialists and businessmen in the top fields of the future. In this future, one of the discoveries of science may be immortality! Future areas and benefits can be unlocked by the community by activating the roadmap. Visit https://nftvampire.club/ for more details.
